    "body": "This PR supersedes https://github.com/KMiri-rs/miri/pull/16 , https://github.com/KMiri-rs/miri/pull/15 , and https://github.com/KMiri-rs/miri/pull/6 .\r\n\r\nA real fix for https://github.com/KMiri-rs/KMiri/issues/19 , https://github.com/KMiri-rs/KMiri/issues/49 , https://github.com/KMiri-rs/KMiri/issues/61 , and https://github.com/KMiri-rs/KMiri/issues/60 .\r\n\r\nGiven the only possible stack allocation is for return value, we reserve the space before all locals are allocated, resume the stack address for return value in before_stack_pop, and check the address is correct in after_stack_pop.\r\n\r\nThe maximum stack footprint is still 6MB,  the same as in https://github.com/KMiri-rs/miri/pull/16.",
